</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*2</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Actuator Portion</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>The actuator portion consists of 3 pressure holding solenoid valves, 3 pressure reduction solenoid valves, 2 pumps and 2 reservoirs.</ptxt>
