<step2>
<ptxt>Speed Sensor</ptxt>
<step3>
<ptxt>The speed sensor detects wheel speed and transmits the appropriate signals to the skid control ECU.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="X105316E01" width="7.106578999in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
